  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Public-sector procurement from 1 January 2021
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Information for public authorities, businesses and other organisations on the outcome for public procurement policy from 1 January 2021.</p>

  </div>
</div>

